content: Feng Jie is a Ph.D. candidate of Agriculture Economics at Applied and Agricluture Economics Department of UW Madison. Her research interests include agriculture economics, Industrial Organization and Finance. She had participated several related projects include U-Metrics and USDA projects etc.
